55:35.248 --> 55:36.624
Honey.

55:36.708 --> 55:39.544
-Why is there no signal?
-Honey, is it working?

55:39.627 --> 55:40.879
There's no signal.

55:43.006 --> 55:46.009
This is an act of terror
against the head of state!

55:46.092 --> 55:47.385
A crime!

55:47.469 --> 55:50.180
Yes, that's right. It's a crime.
I'm a criminal.

55:50.263 --> 55:54.059
